Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:55.86,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,We'are going higher 強烈的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:01:02.25,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,一次次點燃時代的引信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:04.58,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,yeah boom 著火 no matter what you are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:07.67,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,照天燒 burn the fire just set on the 火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:11.55,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,荒唐無稽的上進心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.63,0:01:13.42,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,空中漂浮 現在Time to time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:15.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,一心不亂加堅忍不拔 alright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:17.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:19.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不是孤身一人 let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:22.97,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不要停下 來創造未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:30.36,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,如夜裡的花一般 無人欣賞也綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:36.86,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,從過去繼承的flame 在胸口沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:37.82,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,感受它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:41.37,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,We'are going higher 強烈的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:47.75,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,一次次點燃時代的引信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:51.84,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,將粉碎的命運收回手中
